data.text:
Check out our latest Newsletter (July 3, 2024)!

PLEASE NOTE: The completion of the interior restoration at St. Mary has begun! Due to the intricate work that will be done from floor to ceiling the nave will be filled with scaffolding making it impossible for us to be able to celebrate Mass. That being said, for the entire 4 months that the restoration is scheduled to take - ALL Masses, funerals, baptisms, weddings will be moved to St. John the Baptist.

The New Handicap Access Ramp at St. John the Baptist is available at Weekend Masses until the entire project is complete, currently looking at July 1.

Join Fr. Michael on a pilgrimage to Medjugorje!

Only 19 Spots remain!

Book before August 1, 2024 cut off.

Joshua 1:9!
